data.description: SELLERS ARE OFFERING UP TO $10K IN CLOSING COSTS ASSISTANCE AS WELL AS AN ADDITIONAL $5K TO USE TO BUY DOWN THE INTEREST RATE! Make country living your new home and embark on a journey of wholesome, farm-inspired living. Introducing a serene retreat for those seeking the charm of a country setting. Come experience the essence of rural living at its finest! This 5 bedroom, 4 bath home is waiting for the perfect family. Maybe that family, is you? This 13.26-acre property is your canvas...let your rural dreams unfold here.  Contact an agent today to arrange a viewing and take the first step towards a life of pastoral bliss!!!
